import { Box, Button, Grid, Paper, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function BaseComponent() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Paper>
                <form>
                <Grid container>
                        <Grid item md={12} xs={12}>
                            <Box>
                                <TextField 
                                    variant="outlined" 
                                    label="get a git user information" 
                                    placeholder="search"
                                    fullWidth 
                                />
                            </Box>
                          <Box>
                            <Button variant="contained">
                                Search
                            </Button>
                          </Box>
                        </Grid>
                </Grid>
                </form>
            </Paper>
        </Box>
    )
}
